rows.label: tlk190002_02_msg0001
rows.name:
I really don't think it's a good idea, Rex.
Just refuse... Sounds suspicious to me...

rows.label: tlk190002_02_msg0002
rows.name:
But it's Chairman Bahn's Guild, which is
legit, and I already got the advance...
I'm sure it'll be fine!

rows.label: tlk190002_02_msg0003
rows.name:
High compensation usually implies
a high level of risk, you know...

rows.label: tlk190002_02_msg0004
rows.name:
I strongly suggest you reconsider
whether the job is appropriate for you...

rows.label: tlk190002_02_msg0005
rows.name:
Look, it'll be working alongside Drivers!
It might be a once-in-a-lifetime thing!
Isn't that a valuable experience?

rows.label: tlk190002_02_msg0006
rows.name:
You always tell me experience is
invaluable, right? Well, don't you,
Gramps?
